{"tid":1721511,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好重蹈2014嘅錯","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:33:40.000Z","uid":13936,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67f19725a1df95b0b960e0d45bcdf65d7aac0a4c","tid":1721511,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"唔好令中大變成大台<br />\n特別呢幾日中大無開火<br />\n其他地區仲開緊 <br />\n每日都200幾手足被捕<br />\n但好多物質同手足仍係中大<br />\n<br />\n有入過都知<br />\n中大有啲位好似變咗嘉年華咁<br />\n適當放鬆下係好 但真係唔適宜太過開心<br />\n觀感都唔好睇 <br />\n周同學走咗一星期都無<br />\n隨即有手足被扔落樓㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗下中大守唔守好<br />\n守嘅話應該點 真係好驚變2014"},{"pid":"e731ef2873b7b08440791a6a8d93fe30776bf7e2","tid":1721511,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:22:22.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"c29e283938a9d76c83cf3aaf736acab20f527503","tid":1721511,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"旭日行動 聽朝繼續塞"},{"pid":"6a04a5094ca0b1a70f94a2340ccb59c6c8409798","tid":1721511,"uid":308740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:25:41.000Z","msg":"幫手推<br />\n急!!!!!!!!葵涌邨要人要記者!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721248</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f4d434289d82a80d304b2196dc96a16723a8e4dc","tid":1721511,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ec71bb8cc523b45a330498af14ba8e9dc5febac","tid":1721511,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"其實有幾多手足都有經歷雨傘<br />\n睇住雨傘又最團結，跟住潰散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e078e3d1824f95f73563c97432ff7b70638523","tid":1721511,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有幾多手足都有經歷雨傘<br />\n睇住雨傘由最團